data.description: DISCOVER THE CHARM OF THIS FRESHLY UPDATED, SUN-KISSED 3BED2BATH BRICK GEM, NESTLED IN A JEWEL OF A SPOT JUST 7 MILES FROM FORT NOVOSEL ON HWY 84 IN WOODLANDS SUBDIVISION. YOU'LL FIND YOURSELF CONVENIENTLY LOCATED MERE MINUTES FROM THE BUSTLING ENTERPRISE WALMART AND THE PLETHORA OF SHOPPING DESTINATIONS AND RESTAURANTS IN DOTHAN. STEPPING INSIDE YOUR GAZE WILL BE GREETED BY A BEAUTIFUL FIREPLACE AND BRIGHT WINDOWS THAT INVITE THE OUTSIDE IN. THIS HOME PROUDLY BOASTS BRAND NEW CARPETS IN THE THREE BEDROOMS AND BRAND-NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING IN THE LIVING AND DINING ROOMS, NEWLY PAINTED WALLS THROUGHOUT AND A GREAT NEW ROOF INSTALLED JUST A FEW YEARS AGO FOR YOUR PEACE OF MIND. SELLER IS CONTINUING THE UPGRADES WITH NEW GRANITE COUNTERTOPS TO BE INSTALLED. SAVOR THE WARMTH OF THE DELIGHTFUL GAS FIREPLACE AND ROOMY TWO CAR GARAGE, NOW WITH A NEW GARAGE DOOR OPENER. THE GENEROUS BACK YARD IS A BLANK CANVAS FOR YOUR DREAMS OFFERING SPACE FOR A FUTURE SWIMMING POOL WHILE GIVING YOU PRIVACY WITH ENCOMPASSING WOOD FENCE WITH A NEW GATE. THE INTERIOR IS AWASH WITH NATURAL LIGHT IN THE LIVING ROOM AND KITCHEN. THERE IS ALSO ROOM FOR KITCHEN TABLE AND CHAIRS IN FRONT OF THE BAR TO ENJOY A MORNING SUNSHINE BREAKFAST. . HOME COMES WITH MICROWAVE, OVEN, STOVE, FRIDGE, DISHWASHER AS WELL AS THE WASHER AND DRYER IN THE LAUNDRY ROOM. THE MASTER BATH HAS DUAL VANITY, SEPARATE SHOWER AND WALK-IN CLOSET. THE 2ND BATH ALSO HAS DUAL VANITY. COME MAKE A DEAL QUICKLY TO GIVE INPUT ON CHOOSING THE GRANITE ON THIS PRACTICALLY NEW HOME WITH UPGRADES AND IN A FANTASTIC LOCATION!
